Design a mobile-first and desktop-ready advanced team collaboration platform focused on seamless task and communication management. 
Include login with email/password, sign-up, and password recovery. 
The dashboard displays user projects with concise summaries and easy project creation. 
Each project view offers task lists/cards showing title, assignee, due date, and easy task creation/editing. 
Allow editing task status and details smoothly. 
The user profile screen provides basic settings and logout. 
Prioritize efficient, lightweight mobile interactions for quick task updates and notifications while enabling desktop users with a comprehensive project overview and detailed data entry capabilities.
